    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="如何用Java写Hello-World"><a href="#如何用Java写Hello-World" class="headerlink" title="如何用Java写Hello World"></a>如何用Java写Hello World</h1><p>java作为一款热门的语言，掌握如何用它来写Hello World是非常重要的<br><br>接下来就让我来演示一下</p><blockquote><p>Hello World</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">HelloWorld</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h1 id="完成！"><a href="#完成！" class="headerlink" title="完成！"></a>完成！</h1><p>在上面的例子中，我们新建了一个HelloWorld类，并在主方法中打印了<code>Hello World</code><br><br>怎么样？简单吧，<del>接下来就来开发一个安卓应用吧</del></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
